data.description: Beautiful, spacious, 1-story, corner lot home! Kitchen features granite countertops, beautiful cabinetry, eating area, breakfast area. Extra large family room creates an inviting atmosphere that is both stylish and perfect for entertaining. Big size backyard with wood fence. Ceiling fans throughout. Corner lot location offers plenty of parking around the house for guests. Bedrooms will have new, fresh paint by closing! Fridge stays! Priced to sell makes this the lowest priced home on the market for such a beautiful home!  Won't last long! A must-see! 2023-10-12
